high_descs: Turn around and go to the end table between the window and the couch.
Pick up the newspaper on the right side of the end table.
Turn around and walk past the fireplace and around the furniture, then towards the dining table, make a right at the dining table and walk across the room to the garbage can in the corner.
Put the newspaper in the garbage can.
Turn around and walk back towards the dining table, then make a right at the dining table and go to the dresser the TV in on, to the left of the fireplace.
Pick up the newspaper that is on the right side of the dresser, under the TV.
Turn back around and go towards the table again making a right when you get to the table and back to the garbage can, on the floor, in the corner of the room.
Place the newspaper in the garbage can with the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspaper's in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the end table between the arm chair and the couch.
Pick up the newspaper on the end table.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room to the table, then turn left and walk to the wall, then turn right and face the trash can.
Place the newspaper in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to face the TV stand.
Pick up the newspaper on the TV stand under the TV.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the trash can.
Place the newspaper in the trash can with the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: To gather two newspapers and place them in the trash can.
